    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's a pretty intense start. the \"jungle\" thing is definitely dark. to really lean into that horror vibe, i want to make the residents themselves feel part of the supernatural dread. like, instead of just being in danger, maybe there's something about the culture or the way they act that feels uncanny or menacing to an outsider. how could i describe the people in the crowd to make them seem more intimidating or \"other\"?",
